Can you recall where you where at when you heard of the attack? Do you remeber all of what you did that day and how you felt? It have been five years since that day and I just cant get over that cause to me it feels like it just happened last year. I remeber that day very well I was at work, At the time working on a bus taking care of deaf children. Any-who I was sitting back on the bus a little bored when one of the other drivers who listen to the radio on her trips came on to are radio and said two planes just crashed in the World Trade Centers. I was shocked I thought it was some sick joke till we all could gather around the TV in are lounge area. I could not believe what I was watching. I went home a napped when I woke up I was in shock like was that a bad dream or what? Was that real? I went back to work to finish me day out and the whole day was nothing but silence just about it was the wirdest thing cause in Phoenix so use to hearing planes over head but not that day or a few following it was quiet. I just remeber that night looking up at the sky and only seeing the smog and some stars and just kinda dumb founded. Well any-who that is what I remeber how about you?
